'''敘利亞-瑪拉巴禮天主教巴爾卡德教區'''（{{lang-la|Eparchia Palghatensis}}）是[[東儀天主教|東儀天主教]]的一個[[教區|教區]]（[[敘利亞－瑪拉巴禮教會|敘利亞－瑪拉巴禮]]），位於[[印度|印度]][[喀拉拉邦|喀拉拉邦]]東部[[巴爾卡德縣|巴爾卡德縣]]，受[[敘利亞-瑪拉巴禮天主教德里久爾總教區|德里久爾總教區]]管轄。

教區於1974年6月27日成立<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |date=1974 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |page=472 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-66-1974-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-01-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200116124849/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-66-1974-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-01-16 |language=la}}</ref>，2009年時有教友67,996名（佔轄區總人口百分之9.6），由192名司鐸名管理九十三個堂區。現任主教為{{link-en|雅各伯·馬納托達特|Jacob Manathodath}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 27.06.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/06/27/190627b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-01-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200116123537/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/06/27/190627b.html |archivedate=2020-01-16 |language=en |date=2019-06-27}}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-de|伯多祿·科丘普魯克爾|Peter Kochupuruckal}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Dalle Chiese Orientali, 15.01.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2020/01/15/0027/00059.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-01-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200116112510/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2020/01/15/0027/00059.html |archivedate=2020-01-16 |language=it |date=2020-01-15}}</ref>。

